# 🚚 Migration Rules (Old → New Repo)

These rules guide Cursor AI when migrating code from  
[`bendy_bethc_website`](https://github.com/BethCNC/bendy_bethc_website)  
into [`bendy-bethc-new-design-system`](https://github.com/BethCNC/bendy-bethc-new-design-system).

---

## ✅ Allowed to Copy
- `app/` pages, layouts, and API routes  
- `lib/` (data fetching + Notion integration)  
- `content/` (Markdown/MDX posts)  
- Root files: `middleware.ts`, `next.config.js`, `vercel.json`  
- Footer + navigation JSX structure (but refactor styling)  
- Legacy docs (`COMPONENT_STYLING_SPECS.md`, etc.) into `/docs/legacy/`

---

## ❌ Do Not Copy
- Old `/tokens` folder (use new design system instead)  
- Old `/styles` folder (use utilities + tokens)  
- Any JSX/HTML with:
  - Hardcoded `px` or `rem` font sizes  
  - Hardcoded `#hex` colors  
  - Tailwind-like classes (`mx-auto`, `rounded-lg`, `min-h-screen`)  

---

## 🔄 Migration Transformations

### 1. Replace Hardcoded Styling
```diff
- <button className="bg-blue-500 px-4 py-2 rounded">
+ <button className="btn btn-primary btn-md">
```

### 2. Typography
```diff
- <h2 style={{ fontSize: "28px", fontWeight: 600 }}>
+ <h2 className="text-heading-h2">
```

### 3. Layout & Spacing
```diff
- <div className="mx-auto min-h-screen rounded-lg">
+ <div className="container grid grid-desktop-12 bg-surface-neutral-card">
```

### 4. Footer & Navigation
- Keep structure and links.  
- Replace with semantic tokens:  
  - `text-body-sm`  
  - `bg-surface-neutral-strong`  
  - `btn-link`

---

## 📐 Responsive
- Always mobile-first.  
- Use `grid.css` utilities:  
  - `grid-mobile-4`, `grid-tablet-8`, `grid-desktop-12`  
- Never hardcode breakpoints. Always map to `Responsive-*.json`.  

---

## 🔒 Accessibility
- Replace inline `onClick` icons with `<button aria-label="...">`.  
- All icon-only buttons must include `aria-label`.  
- Focus styles must use:  
  ```css
  outline: 2px solid var(--border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
  ```

---

## ✅ Final Checklist
- [ ] No hardcoded colors or px values remain  
- [ ] All components styled via semantic tokens/utilities  
- [ ] Navigation + footer links preserved  
- [ ] Blog + content migration works with Notion + MDX  
- [ ] Old `tokens/` and `styles/` excluded  
